&lt;p&gt;I have used this command to generate the PDF-file:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;pdflatex latex.tex -output-format&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;pdf
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="gnuplot"&gt;gnuplot&lt;/h2&gt;
